Sunhawk leans close and whispers to Drillbit.

Sunhawk:  In that case if it was my choice I'd get
ride of you here and now, but Commander Talos has
taken a liking to you Preds.  He's talking to another
one right now.  Still, don't expect the luxury
treatment.  If your sides hurt then it's from my
talons when I brought you here.

He smiles slyly and walks away.
